      "updated": 1774298612148,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": " Flatland is a country with a number of cities, some of which have space stations. \nCities are numbered consecutively and each has a road of 1Km length connecting it \nto the next city. It is not a circular route, so the first city doesn't connect with \nthe last city. Determine the maximum distance from any city to its nearest space station. ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": " Flatland is a country with a number of cities, some of which have space stations. \nCities are numbered consecutively and each has a road of 1Km length connecting it \nto the next city. It is not a circular route, so the first city doesn't connect with \nthe last city. Determine the maximum distance from any city to its nearest space station. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
